findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function removeStakers() uses a loop to remove stakers from the list and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including transferring ownership, updating staking limits, changing various parameters, resetting the contract, and withdrawing tokens.
